title: Recall Notification Report 045-2016 (Pulled Pork Products)
summary: WASHINGTON, May 27, 2016 Burgers Ozark County Cured, a California, Mo. establishment, is recalling approximately 150 pounds of pulled pork products due to misbranding, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
